1. *Vidjet* ću te sutra u parku. (I will see you tomorrow in the park.)

2. Šta ćeš *vidjeti* kad odeš u inostranstvo? (What will you see when you go abroad?)

3. *Vidje* li ona mog brata? (Did she see my brother?)

4. Nisam *vidjela* njegovo lice. (I didn't see his face.)

5. *Vidjeli* smo da je sve u redu. (We saw that everything was okay.)

6. Šta si *vidjela* kad si išla u grad? (What did you see when you went to town?)